- _On C3/C4, the comparison arm experiences {wedge / lost-work / agent-abandon} events at rate {Wilson CI}; maw stays at 0 with Wilson 95% UB ≤ {table}._
- _The crossover from OVERKILL to HOSTILE occurs in {C1..C3} band; the band's width is reported per pre-reg §4.3 (never collapsed to a point if MIXED)._

## TIE_REGIME

_Cells within the pre-registered materiality margin (×1.15 ratio for efficiency; ±0.10 gap for rates)._

_(no cells in this regime)_

## NO_DATA

_Cells where the metric was not measurable (e.g. `MockAgent` cost is `Unavailable`)._

